{"tid":2422051,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇返工兄弟試過去屙屎見到公司廁板有屎跡？","createTime":"2021-02-25T02:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T03:39:05.000Z","uid":40930,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a017a30bb3e9b86ef41537620496ae0d8ef81bb1","tid":2422051,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"返工屙屎都係最開心嘅時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但大家有冇試過揀好一格入去屙屎嗰陣，見到一笪屎跡係神聖嘅廁板上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰刻真係屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/linguistic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲所謂同事屙完屎唔望下後面不止，究竟佢地識唔識得屙屎？ 屙屎角度都搞唔掂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">你老母咁辛苦生你出嚟，未學行就識屙屎，咁大個人先嚟話唔識屙屎？唔係啊哇？</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各路屙屎英雄，記住返工屙完屎要check check 廁板<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79d6468b74f1425ce3c500d795b250956446ab0","tid":2422051,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"試過 四級爛屎 除唔切  成舊屎柯左上 板上面 即刻去下一格"},{"pid":"9fef8504f4d70d0e227df971279c394f8fd477ec","tid":2422051,"uid":64253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:34:18.000Z","msg":"成舊屎係廁所板上面都試過 但冇人認領<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd74dd947777bd5c75b159a79d0d23e0c4533f0","tid":2422051,"uid":206834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"試過太急 唔小心一除褲就好似火箭爆發咁噴曬出黎<br />\n想話用念力忍多一陣都已經太遲 d屎同廁所好似有磁力咁"},{"pid":"fc332e3a462fdf41e77d28c5ac7be7a8eb6c577e","tid":2422051,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:39:05.000Z","msg":"熱定凍？"}]}